title: Ariel Winter keeps things simple in jeans and a t-shirt | Daily Mail Online
text: Share The pretty young actress coordinated with matching white slip on shoes. It appears as though she drew on them herself, with each shoe featuring a different design. She said goodbye to the people around her as she clutched her Celine bag in one hand and a pair of keys in the other. Little bit of sex appeal: The 19-year-old star let her lacy black bra peek out of the top of her loose white t-shirt Ever the glamorous star, Ariel made her eyes pop with long eyelashes and dark liner around her eyes The only pop of color seemed to be the dark blue fuzzy poof the key chain. Ever the glamorous star, Ariel made her eyes pop with long eyelashes and dark liner around her eyes. She appeared to have very little foundation on her face, allowing her natural complexion to shine through. Her dark brown hair was sleek and straight around her shoulders and she tucked it behind her ears to keep it out of her eyes. Cool ride: She got into her white Range Rover after exchanging pleasantries with those around her and ended her work for the day She got into her white Range Rover after exchanging pleasantries with those around her and ended her work for the day. The actress is fresh off her SAG award appearance with her 29-year-old boyfriend Levi Meaden. The TV star looked gorgeous in a plunging semi sheer lace gold gown and was not shy about PDA with her man on the red carpet. Cute couple: The actress recently attended the SAG awards with boyfriend Levi Meaden Although her outfit Wednesday was relatively modest, she has complained in the past about people calling her out for posting sexy pictures online. Ariel still doesn't understand why she gets backlash for posting images of her scantily-clad ensembles to her 3.6M social media followers. 'They kind of glorify and objectify a lot of the things that I do, and I wish people would just see me as the normal 18-year-old that I am,' she previously lamented to Self magazine. Modest? The actress has complained about people calling her out for posting sexy snaps on social media 'I'm doing the same things that everybody my age is doing...people are taking it and making it [seem] like I’m doing stuff that is crazy when really I’m just being me. I wish people would see that.' The aspiring federal prosecutor graduated from Campbell Hall School last June, and she plans on beginning her pre-law studies at UCLA this fall. Fans can catch Ariel Alex Dunphy on the eighth season of their mockumentary sitcom, which airs Wednesdays on ABC.
